  "texts": [
    "Reducing operator workload while maintaining safety is discussed in Section 6.6. v.) We discuss why some of the works in existing literature are not compatible for comparison with the detection accuracy of the proposed anomaly detector, and its implications for reporting experimental results in this work (see Section 6.7).The paper is organised as follows.",
    "Section 2 provides the problem context and discusses the threat model.",
    "Section 3 presents the detector solution.",
    "The solution is extended in Section 4.",
    "Experiments are carried out and results presented in Section 5."
  ]
}